{"_comment":"Gemini CLI spec-ACP fixture SKELETON (Cohort-A readiness). Drives the Generic ACP Framework's Protocol+Acceptance gates in-process via the provider-agnostic replay agent. NOT a recording of the real gemini --experimental-acp binary — the real wire contract is UNVERIFIED and MUST be confirmed against the real binary at Gemini CLI's own live validation. Shape mirrors the reconciled spec ACP lifecycle: initialize -> authenticate -> session/new -> session/prompt (agent_message_chunk + tool_call + request_permission + terminal stopReason)."}
{"on":"initialize","emit":[{"jsonrpc":"2.0","id":"__ID__","result":{"protocolVersion":1,"agentInfo":{"name":"gemini-cli","version":"skeleton"},"agentCapabilities":{"promptCapabilities":{"image":true}},"authMethods":[{"type":"env_var","id":"gemini-api-key","name":"Use GEMINI_API_KEY"}]}}]}
